name: My Apartment!
description: My apartment, just like the title says! (DOOM ][) This is my first attempt at making a PWAD, so be kind. BTW, my apartment is in Tampa, FL, near the Univ. of South Florida, where I am a Mech. Engineering Grad. Student. I started with the intent of making a DM only level, but put some monstas and an exit in for the hell of it.
